Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.88,0:07:45.06,IN_CH_EP07_M1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}…也傷害到自己
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.51,0:07:51.55,IN_CH_EP07_M1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,360)\blur3}即便如此 我也不會放開牽著的手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:13.53,IN_JP_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}居場所を探していた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:19.30,IN_JP_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}幸せを探してた　なくしたくなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:28.18,IN_JP_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}一瞬一瞬　必死にしがみつく
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:35.31,IN_JP_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}僕にはそれ　しかできない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:43.82,IN_JP_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}光の中舞う君は　遠すぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:48.51,IN_JP_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}つかめない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:54.26,IN_JP_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}おこったこと　泣いたこと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:16:00.82,IN_JP_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}何がそこで　見えていたの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:08.24,IN_JP_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}その羽を　ただ　見つめてた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.24,0:16:14.08,IN_JP_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}人間になりたいって　つぶやいた君に
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:20.09,IN_JP_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}かける言葉も　優しさも違って
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:26.20,IN_JP_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}幸せだって　同じじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:30.93,IN_JP_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}誰もが最初から
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:37.83,IN_JP_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}それでも身体をひらいて　手を伸ばしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:44.28,IN_JP_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}何度間違えても　これが心の叫びだから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:49.40,IN_JP_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}息をして　涙する
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:57.97,IN_JP_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}人間になりたい
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.64,0:15:13.53,IN_CH_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}我一直在尋找歸宿
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.53,0:15:19.30,IN_CH_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}也在尋找幸福 不想失去
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.30,0:15:28.18,IN_CH_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}每個瞬間都拼著命 緊緊抓住不放手
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.18,0:15:35.31,IN_CH_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}這就是我唯一能做的
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.21,0:15:43.82,IN_CH_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}你舞動在光芒之中 離我那麼遙遠
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.05,0:15:48.51,IN_CH_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}讓我無法觸及
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.51,0:15:54.26,IN_CH_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}我們的經歷 我們的淚水
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.26,0:16:00.82,IN_CH_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}其中能看出什麼呢
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.45,0:16:08.24,IN_CH_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}我依然緊盯著那對翅膀
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.24,0:16:14.08,IN_CH_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}你低語著 想要成為人類
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.08,0:16:20.09,IN_CH_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}我找不到該說的話 關心的方法
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.09,0:16:26.20,IN_CH_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}其實幸福 也各自不同
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.00,0:16:30.93,IN_CH_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}大家從來都是這樣
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.56,0:16:37.83,IN_CH_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}即便如此 我也想奮不顧身伸出手
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.83,0:16:44.28,IN_CH_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}就算錯再多次 這也是我內心的吶喊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.28,0:16:49.40,IN_CH_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}我呼吸著 流下淚水
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.21,0:16:57.97,IN_CH_EP07_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}想要成為人類
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:07.63,IN_JP_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}悴んだ心　ふるえる眼差し
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:13.97,IN_JP_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}世界で僕は　ひとりぼっちだった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:25.48,IN_JP_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}散ることしか知らない春は毎年冷たくあしらう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:29.81,IN_JP_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}暗がりの中　一方通行に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:36.34,IN_JP_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}ただただ　言葉を書き殴って
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:44.19,IN_JP_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}期待するだけむなしいと分かっていても
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.19,0:19:47.66,IN_JP_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}救いを求め続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:51.63,IN_JP_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}せつなくていとおしい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:55.46,IN_JP_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}今ならば分かる気がする
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:59.43,IN_JP_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}しあわせでくるおしい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:03.02,IN_JP_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}あの日泣けなかった僕を
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:09.90,IN_JP_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}光はやさしく連れ立つよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:14.21,IN_JP_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}雲間をぬってきらりきらり
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:17.70,IN_JP_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}心満たしては溢れ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:21.41,IN_JP_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}いつしか頬をきらりきらり
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:25.24,IN_JP_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}熱く熱く濡らしてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:32.63,IN_JP_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}君の手はどうしてこんなにも温かいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.63,0:20:42.18,IN_JP_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}ねえお願い　どうかこのまま離さないでいて
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.77,0:19:07.63,IN_CH_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}內心冰冷僵硬 目光顫抖
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.63,0:19:13.97,IN_CH_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}我在這世界孤單一人
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.97,0:19:25.48,IN_CH_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}只懂落花的春天 每年依舊對我冷漠
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.11,0:19:29.81,IN_CH_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}黑暗之中 我從不回頭
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.81,0:19:36.34,IN_CH_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}只是埋著頭 狠狠塗下詞句
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.34,0:19:44.19,IN_CH_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}即使我知道越期待就越失落
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.19,0:19:47.66,IN_CH_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}但還是不斷尋找救贖
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.17,0:19:51.63,IN_CH_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}難過卻令人喜愛
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.63,0:19:55.46,IN_CH_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}我現在開始明白了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.46,0:19:59.43,IN_CH_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}幸福又痴迷其中
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.43,0:20:03.02,IN_CH_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}那天的我不懂如何哭泣
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.02,0:20:09.90,IN_CH_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}一道溫柔的光芒攜我踏上旅程
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.70,0:20:14.21,IN_CH_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}光芒穿過雲間 閃閃發亮
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.21,0:20:17.70,IN_CH_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}填滿我的心 直到滿溢
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.70,0:20:21.41,IN_CH_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}不知何時臉頰晶瑩閃爍
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.41,0:20:25.24,IN_CH_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}一片溫熱浸潤開來
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.24,0:20:32.63,IN_CH_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}你的手為什麼會如此溫暖？
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.63,0:20:42.18,IN_CH_EP07_M3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3\fax-0.1}求你別離開 就這樣一直牽著我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.43,0:02:05.60,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&}弄られて垂れ流す　音のない音
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.60,0:02:10.99,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&}遍く　名前を捨てたのね　あなたのモザイクが泣いてる
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.99,0:02:15.95,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,can not, can not, not, not, not deny 紛れもなく真実
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.87,0:02:20.41,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,さあ　預けて　回帰するように
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.83,0:02:26.54,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,エネルギーはサイクル　そう　いまは無重力
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.54,0:02:33.88,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,象徴的なパレード　この月夜に仰げよ仰げ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.47,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,‘completeness’
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.47,0:02:39.31,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&}嗚呼　命の灯を掲げ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.68,0:02:44.02,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&}KiLLKiSS judy.., KiLLKiSS jude.., KiLLKiSS juda.., 欺いて
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.02,0:02:49.19,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&}KiLLKiSS judy.., KiLLKiSS jude.., KiLLKiSS juda.., 抱きしめて
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.19,0:02:57.03,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&}ねぇ　無防備だね　美しい戯れに　人は壊れてゆく
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.74,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H20105B&}可笑しいわね
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.20,0:03:13.09,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H20105B&}そう　このまま　壊れて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:15.95,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H431FAF&\1a&HFF&\bord5}can not, can not, not, not, not deny 紛れもなく真実
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.87,0:02:20.41,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H431FAF&\1a&HFF&\bord5}さあ　預けて　回帰するように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:26.54,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H431FAF&\1a&HFF&\bord5}エネルギーはサイクル　そう　いまは無重力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:33.88,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H431FAF&\1a&HFF&\bord5}象徴的なパレード　この月夜に仰げよ仰げ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.47,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H431FAF&\1a&HFF&\bord5}‘completeness’
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.74,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H431FAF&\1a&HFF&\bord3}可笑しいわね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:13.09,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H431FAF&\1a&HFF&\bord3}そう　このまま　壊れて
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.43,0:02:05.60,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&}命運玩弄之下 無聲之音橫流
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.60,0:02:10.99,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&}你已捨棄一切名義 只剩模糊殘像哭泣
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.99,0:02:15.95,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,無法 無法否認 毫無疑問的真實
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.87,0:02:20.41,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,交給我吧 從此走向回歸
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.83,0:02:26.54,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,能量不斷循環 重力已經消失
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.54,0:02:33.88,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,代表性的遊行 於月夜之下祈求
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.47,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,「完美無缺」
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.47,0:02:39.31,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&}高舉生命燈火
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.68,0:02:44.02,OP_CH,,0,0,15,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&\fnA-OTF Ryumin Pr6N U-KL\fs60}KiLLKiSS judy.., KiLLKiSS jude.., KiLLKiSS juda.., {\fnFZYaSong-H-GBK\fs52}欺騙一切
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.02,0:02:49.19,OP_CH,,0,0,15,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&\fnA-OTF Ryumin Pr6N U-KL\fs60}KiLLKiSS judy.., KiLLKiSS jude.., KiLLKiSS juda.., {\fnFZYaSong-H-GBK\fs52}緊擁入懷
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.19,0:02:57.03,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&}真是毫無防備 美麗的嬉鬧之中 人走向毀壞
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.74,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H20105B&}如此可笑
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.20,0:03:13.09,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H20105B&}就這樣 走向毀滅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:15.95,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H431FAF&\1a&HFF&\bord5}無法 無法否認 毫無疑問的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.87,0:02:20.41,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H431FAF&\1a&HFF&\bord5}交給我吧 從此走向回歸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:26.54,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H431FAF&\1a&HFF&\bord5}能量不斷循環 重力已經消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:33.88,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H431FAF&\1a&HFF&\bord5}代表性的遊行 於月夜之下祈求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.47,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H431FAF&\1a&HFF&\bord5}「完美無缺」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.74,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H431FAF&\1a&HFF&\bord3}如此可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:13.09,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H431FAF&\1a&HFF&\bord3}就這樣 走向毀滅吧
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.67,0:22:05.39,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(640,640)}白銀の糸を伝い　想い　手繰り寄せてた
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.39,0:22:15.48,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(640,640)}その果てで妊る月　抱きしめたなら
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.28,0:22:30.29,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(640,640)}待っているの　太陽から夜が堕ちてくるのを
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.29,0:22:41.09,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(640,640)}ねぇ　その果てで満たしてよ　届く気がするの
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.09,0:22:50.85,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(640,640)}もつれたまま　踊る Geogette Me, Geogette You まわる
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.85,0:23:06.28,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(640,640)}痛むほどに　ほら　煌めくドレスを纏いながら
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.99,0:23:08.91,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}everlastin’ ever..
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.16,0:23:13.83,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}darlin’ ever, ever..
